    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/clayfield" style="color:#b98229;">Clayfield</a>, <a href="/suburbs/lutwyche" style="color:#b98229;">Lutwyche</a>, <a href="/suburbs/nundah" style="color:#b98229;">Nundah</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#b98229;">Kedron</a>.</p>
